TEXTS.ITEM: * In most case, this pop-up appears because a name conflict. The function module &FUNCTION&, that you're trying to import in this system, already exists in the function group &GROUP&. You should cancel and remove naming conflict. You can do this either : * - in your container file (XML) : rename function &FUNCTION& in function group &CURRENT_G& * - in SAP system : rename function module &FUNCTION& in your SAP System to allow import of this new function. * * If function is the same and you just want to move it. Choose 'Yes' to confirm deletion.
